Cold       4 - 5   <= 5     + 5
Average    6 - 8   6 - 24   + 0
Hot        9 - 10  >= 25    - 5
Very Hot   11 +    >= 35    - 10

In addition the following modifier applies:
The Adept is standing on Ice or Snow in an area where it is in
abundance      + 5
