\emph{Effects:}
d123 6
a128 7
This spell extinguishes all fires within a chosen 5
foot (+5 / Rank) diameter sphere, all of which must be within
the spells range, by smothering them with ice crystals.
Magical fires are not affected. This spell is identical to the
Fire College "Extinguish Fire Spell", except that the effect
is achieved by physical means (this is merely a cosmetic
difference).
a139 1
\emph{Effects:}
d141 6
a146 6
The Adept may freeze one object of up to 5 lb. (+5 /
Rank). This freezing will protect the object from decay while
the duration lasts. While frozen the object will be as cold as
ice to the touch and will drip slightly from condensation.
When the duration has expired the object will defrost at the
rate of 1 minute per pound of weight.
