applicable), than the size of the Adept.  No more than 1 hex
(+1 / 2 full Ranks), may be cleared per pulse in this manner. 
This effect moves with the Adept.  The Adept may lean in order
to direct the path up or down.  Note that the walls and roof
of a tunnel through snow or ice are merely packed snow and do
not confer any particular structural support or stability. 
See 7.4, Travel on or through Snow, for additional detail.
