10' (+1 each dimension / Rank) cube. Any entity within this
cube which fails to resist will suffer D-4 (+1 / 2 full Ranks)
points of magical cold damage per pulse. Creatures of fire
(efreet, salamander or elemental) take half damage even if
they resist.
