or the Adept may target and kill 1 individual plant (+1 /
Rank).  There is no visible effect, but death due to frostbite
occurs at the time of casting and no amount of non-magical
effort will revive plants affected by this spell.  Plants that
are especially resistant to cold may be entitled to a passive
resistance roll versus the spell's effects.

