\emph{Storage:} Investment, Ward, Magical Trap, Potion \\
a420 1
\emph{Effects:}
d422 16
a437 18
The target of this spell is placed in suspended
animation for up to (Rank \x Rank) days (minimum 1) as
specified by the Adept.  At Rank 20 there is no maximum and
the Adept may choose any duration.  All bodily functions
including ageing, are suspended for the duration of the spell
and the target feels cool to the touch. The target is immune
to cold and suffocation, and takes no more damage from
existing injuries while this spell is in effect. Additional
injuries will still effect the target, but any damage that
would occur due to bleeding, poison etc. is ignored while this
spell is in effect. When the spell duration runs out, or the
spell is dispelled, the target awakens with physical strength
reduced by 1 /  full week hibernated and begins to suffer from
any existing injuries and conditions (poison, disease, shock,
bleeding and suchlike). Physical strength may be regained at a
rate of 1 point per day, and is not reduced below 1. Entities
that naturally hibernate suffer -20 to their Magic Resistance
vs. this spell.
